{"tid":1464003,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"贊成阻塞既就去離境大堂，唔支持既就去入境大堂做文宣","createTime":"2019-08-13T14:14:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T14:17:31.000Z","uid":9257,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9bb51da2563e1cf291feb5e7740050e15b85d877","tid":1464003,"uid":9257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:14:12.000Z","msg":"聽日現場睇下邊邊多人？係連登嘈餐懵都唔係辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06f5309002b50285784197aea457eaaad902cf59","tid":1464003,"uid":68471,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:15:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">塞旅客一定要塞如果唔係出機場做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n塞嘅話，留返一個counter/閘口出黎，放一條極細既路出黎，由佢地排條好長既隊，排都排一兩粒鐘。其他路block Q曬，咁你就人道了，無位比人入了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n圍師必缺，你唔使塞死，已經塞死。</span>"},{"pid":"f0331aafd2789b4eb8c26a6af3d79d992986fe88","tid":1464003,"uid":9257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:15:46.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"903c60ff20eccf9f05f42ef46930bad7fed64574","tid":1464003,"uid":258055,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:15:55.000Z","msg":"根本鬼一直都存在 只不過星期日一次過爆哂出黎 點解要咁做? 因為團結同信任係我地堅持咁耐既原因 某人想制造猜疑 令我地唔再互信 以後前線做某d唔岩心水既野 你地就話佢係鬼 和理非唔再行出黎 場運動慢慢就會散 <br />\n<br />\n鬼無可能捉得哂 只要堅持自己相信既做法 鬼根本阻唔到你"},{"pid":"5ece08df3d6f18c9e85c865b8c95cab30387a55a","tid":1464003,"uid":9257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:16:00.000Z","msg":"An eye for an eye"},{"pid":"18e87e049e501bf8895348d50ef895232256a18e","tid":1464003,"uid":9257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:17:31.000Z","msg":"721"}]}